My partner and I have traveled to Puerto Rico a number of times and the only place in NYC that can compare to the pernil and food quality of Guavate, Cayey in PR is this spot.. you will never go wrong!!  We are locals in the neighborhood and eat there quite often, nearly five times a week. If you like chicharron, morcilla and pernil this is the place for you ☺ Hector and his wife along with two sons cook and run the business. The service is very personal and homie. Jesus the youngest son is the best! He provides quality interaction and makes you feel right at home. Compare to other local places you might spend an extra dollar or two but its worth every single cent!!!!   Take the trip, trust me you will not regret it!
